1999;;In Dreams;;American;;Neil Jordan;;Annette Bening, Katie Sagona, Aidan Quinn, Robert Downey Jr., Stephen Rea;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/In_Dreams_(film);;Claire Cooper (Bening) is a suburban housewife and mother who illustrates children's stories, and is married to an airline pilot (Aidan Quinn). Her world unravels when her daughter is kidnapped and brutally murdered.<br><br>Claire is haunted by her daughter's murderer, a serial killer named Vivian Thompson (Downey). She has several visions of the murders he commits next. When doctors diagnose her as psychotic, Claire is committed to a mental institution. She receives a vision of Vivian kidnapping another child, and escapes to track him down and stop him from killing again.